It was a thriller of a match when Sri Lanka and Afghanistan faced each other in the first ODI. Sri Lanka posted a massive total of 381 runs on the board and Pathum Nissanka scored a brilliant double-century in the process. During the chase, Afghanistan lost five wickets in quick succession but a superb partnership between Azmatullah Omarzai and Mohammad Nabi took them near the target. In the end, it was Sri Lanka who sealed a victory after winning by 42 runs.

In today's video, we delve into the escalating epidemic of myopia, a condition affecting vision clarity, that has seen a dramatic rise in rates from 4.5% to over 21% among individuals aged 5-15 years in India over the past two decades. snippet.description:
रउवा लोगन जैसे पॉवरएक्सप्रेस पकड़ के आरा बलिया के सैर करत बानी, वैसे हम सबके PowerStar #PawanSingh के गाना के भी हर घर घर बजवाय दा |

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:  @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Credits:
Title - Arrah Ballia Chhapra
Hindi “आरा बलिया छपरा”
Singer :- Pawan Singh And Anupma Yadav
Hindi - पवन सिंह और अनुपमा यादव
Lyrics :- Vinay Bihari 
Music :- Shubham Raj (SBR)
Feat - Ritu Singh 
Additional Vocal- Arohi Bharadwaj
Director & Choreographer:- Lakkie Vishwakarma
DOP:- Yogesh Singh 
Editor:-  Rishu Singh 
Assistant Choreographer:- Suresh And Ashu
DI:- Rohit Singh

Lyrics
Female
भोजपुरिया मरद बड़ी देला दरद
सुन ले हम बानी रहे हरदम बेपरद - २
हम नाही मोलब अयसन ख़तरा -२ 
Male 
दिल वाला हवे सुन ला ऐ गोरिया
आरा बलिया हो छपरा -२ 

Male
प्यार करे वाला अयसन मरद ना पाइबु
मान जैबु लोहा जहिया माँग भरबैबु -२

Female
जाना तानी छोर देबा मस्ती उठा के
दु चार दिन ला हमके दुलहिन बना के 
नाही चाही तोहरा जयसन भतरा -१ 

Male 
रंगीला हवे सुन ल ऐ गोरिया
आरा बलिया हो छपरा -
दिल वाला हवे सुन ला ऐ गोरिया आरा बलिया हो छपरा 

Male
बहियाँ में आ के देखा जियरा जुड़ाई
आरा बलिया छपरा वाला छोर दा लड़ाई -२

Female
बतिया तनी के क़हत बाड़ा ऐ राजा
जयसे मन करे हमरा जिया में समा जा
गावा संघे पवन पिया पचरा -२ 
Male - 
मस्तिला हवे सुन ला ऐ गोरिया 
आरा बलिया हो छपरा
दिल वाला हवे सुन ला ऐ गोरिया 
आरा बलिया हो छपरा

snippet.title: 'Boss Vs Boss😎' Triple H REJECTS The Rock, Roman Reigns Vs Cody Rhodes - WWE Smackdown Highlights
snippet.description:
Topics Covered In Video-
1) WWE Smackdown 9 February 2024 highlights & full show results in Hindi
2) Triple H takes shots at The Rock
3) Roman Reigns will defend his title against Cody Rhodes
4) The Rock & Roman Reigns to return to Smackdown
5) WWE Elimination Chamber 2024 qualifying matches

#wwe #smackdown #therock #romanreigns #tripleh 

'Boss Vs Boss😎' Triple H REJECTS The Rock, Roman Reigns Vs Cody Rhodes - WWE Smackdown Highlights

Experience the explosive WWE Smackdown highlights from February 9, 2024, featuring heart-stopping action and unforgettable moments. Immerse yourself in the full show, witnessing electrifying clashes and high-flying maneuvers that define Smackdown. Watch as The Rock makes his long-awaited return, igniting the arena with his unmatched charisma. Witness the epic showdown between The Rock and Triple H, as old rivalries reignite. Feel the seismic impact as Roman Reigns and The Rock unite, forming an unstoppable force. Don't miss a second of the adrenaline-pumping excitement as WWE Smackdown delivers another unforgettable episode packed with thrills and drama.

The segment featuring Triple H, Nick Aldis, Adam Pearce, and Drew McIntyre kicked off with a bang, setting the stage for an electrifying night on SmackDown. Triple H, the authority figure, took center stage, asserting his dominance and clarifying the path to WrestleMania. With unwavering confidence, he declared the main event matchup and made it clear that he's the ultimate decision-maker.
Nick Aldis stepped in to announce the next big challenge, shifting focus to the World Heavyweight Championship scene. With a united front, WWE Management laid out plans for an Elimination Chamber match to determine the challenger for Seth Rollins. This decision showcased the collaborative effort behind the scenes to ensure a thrilling road to WrestleMania.
Adam Pearce then outlined the lineup for the Elimination Chamber, featuring top-tier superstars vying for a shot at championship glory. The intense competition and high stakes set the stage for an epic showdown.
Drew McIntyre, fueled by determination and a desire to prove himself, made his presence known. With a fiery speech, he laid out his path to WrestleMania, promising to overcome all obstacles and emerge victorious for the WWE Universe.
The action heated up with the first match of the night, a hard-hitting showdown between McIntyre and AJ Styles. The back-and-forth battle showcased the raw athleticism and tenacity of both competitors, with McIntyre ultimately securing the win and advancing in the Elimination Chamber race.
As the night unfolded, backstage interviews provided insight into the mindset of other contenders like Sami Zayn and Randy Orton, each determined to seize their moment on the road to WrestleMania.
The tension continued to build with confrontations between rival factions and personal revelations, setting the stage for future clashes and storyline developments.
Overall, the segment featuring Triple H, Nick Aldis, Adam Pearce, and Drew McIntyre delivered a thrilling mix of intrigue, competition, and anticipation as the journey to WrestleMania reached new heights.

Episode 4003: Online Scams Se Bacho
--------------------------------------------------------
The Gokuldham men gather for a soda session, but Popatlal is absent, and he feels left out upon arrival. The conversation shifts to the risks of online shopping, discussing how some companies deceive customers. Meanwhile, Bhide expresses his desire to purchase a gold chain for Sonu.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: We Make Diesel At Home - Bio-Diesel...हम अमीर बनने वाले है🤑
snippet.description:
How To Make Bio Diesel At Home From Vegetable Oil...

 SUBSCRIBE : https://youtube.com/MRINDIANHACKER?sub_confirmation=1

FOLLOW KARLO 😘
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/dilraj_singh_rawat
Twitter : https://www.x.com/MR_INDIANHACKER
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/mrindianhacker00.

Thanks For Watching, Love You Titanium Army.

Biodiesel is a renewable, biodegradable fuel manufactured domestically from vegetable oils, animal fats, or recycled restaurant grease. Biodiesel meets both the biomass-based diesel and overall advanced biofuel requirement of the Renewable Fuel Standard.

How To Make Biodiesel From Vegetable Oil - 

How to Make Biodiesel

1. You want to prepare the biodiesel in a room that is at least 60 degrees C because the chemical reaction will not proceed to completion if the temperature is too low.

2. label all your containers as "Toxic—Only Use for Making Biodiesel.

3. Wear Protective Gloves And Other Apparatus 

4. Mix the methanol and sodium hydroxide until the sodium hydroxide has completely dissolved then add vegetable oil ( 60 Degree C ) to this mixture.

5. Continue blending this mixture Slowly for 20 to 30 minutes.

6. Pour the mixture into a widemouthed jar. You will see the liquid start to separate out into layers. The bottom layer will be glycerin. The top layer is biodiesel.

7. Allow at least a couple of hours for the mixture to fully separate. You want to keep the top layer as your biodiesel fuel. If you like, you can keep the glycerin for other projects. You can either carefully pour off the biodiesel or use a pump or baster to pull the biodiesel off of the glycerin.

8. You Should Wash Biodiesel at least 5 times with water.

Biodiesel can be used in several ways, but it's important to consider your specific context and vehicle compatibility before trying it.

Compatibility: Most modern diesel engines can handle low blends of biodiesel (B5 or B20) without modification. Check your vehicle owner's manual for specific recommendations. Higher blends (B50, B100) may require modifications and are not always recommended.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

GAAMI Making Video on UV Creations. #Gaami latest telugu movie starring Vishwak Sen, Chandini Chowdary and others chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant and reclusive aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare human condition- the one that will be cured, only when he can confront and conquers the haunting ironical questions of his life.

snippet.description:
Neerparavai (transl. Seabird) is a 2012 Indian Tamil-language drama film written and directed by Seenu Ramasamy and produced by Udhayanidhi Stalin. It stars Vishnu and Sunaina, and Nandita Das plays the older version of the latter's character. Saranya Ponvannan, Samuthirakani, Varsha Ashwathi, and Anupama Kumar play supporting roles. The music is composed by N. R. Raghunanthan with cinematography by Balasubramaniem and editing by Kasi Viswanathan.

Cast - Vishnu Vishal, Sunaina, Samuthirakani, Saranya Ponvannan & Nandita das

snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 1000 Motichoor Laddu using crushed pearls. Normally, laddu is made with Boondi, but Motichoor laddu is made using smashed Boondi. That is why Moticoor Laddu is special and so soft.

The taste is Yummy!

snippet.description:
నా ఇతర వీడియోలు 
ఆలోచింపదగినవి మరియు ఆచరింపదగినవి:

ఎన్నాళ్ళో వేచిన ఉదయం: https://youtu.be/e_X5WcE0ONY
ఆలోచనలు ఆచరణలోకి వస్తే:https://youtu.be/nqC3d4_HtVQ
నేను అమ్మ నా బడి: https://youtu.be/QFCTuiWCem8
కళ్ళ ముందు కదిలే పుస్తకాలు:https://youtu.be/vI5IGyJJ3WY
భయానికి అభయం ఇస్తే:https://youtu.be/unnrCv4rfOE

oui అంటే:https://youtu.be/fboXQtaUPcY
గోమాత రాకతో కళ:https://youtu.be/4Ws8Q-oFLlk

బుడి బుడి అడుగుల గంగ బుజ్జి:https://youtu.be/srB7MnZ0tJE
గంగమ్మ అల్లరికి అంతే లేదు: https://youtu.be/Gxkqrju5AdU

గోవులతో జీవించడం అదృష్టం:https://youtu.be/hodxzasuL-A
https://youtu.be/g9Xn4BLb0ZI
https://youtu.be/hnmYiauz5ow


ఆరోగ్యకరమైనవి:
https://youtu.be/I3jCVN1ox1s
https://youtu.be/iKaLA9_u0GE
https://youtu.be/I3jCVN1ox1s

ఉపయోగకరమైనవి: 
రేకుల షెడ్డు పైన డాబా నిర్మాణం:https://youtu.be/68gVBYOEdw0
300 sqft షెడ్డు నిర్మాణం:https://youtu.be/U2_ChQRcmMk
పొలంలో చిన్న ఇల్లు కట్టుకోవాలంటే:https://youtu.be/yi6fgIIy6qE
తక్కువ ఖర్చుతో సోలార్ ఫెన్స్ :https://youtu.be/LqAQ0QGe9IE

గృహోపకరణమైనవి:
డిష్ వాషర్ ఎలా పనిచేస్తుంది?https://youtu.be/cNohtXmMJGg
                                                    https://youtu.be/-OVEnexp_ts
ఫ్రిడ్జ్ ను ఎలా సర్దుకోవాలి?https://youtu.be/n4Yt3Bnbh0U
అన్ని రకాల వంట పాత్రలపై అవగాహన: https://youtu.be/AtCOug0CjAA
ఎయిర్ fryer ఉపయోగాలు:https://youtu.be/Zs-lqortG5k
గ్యాస్ హాబ్ vs గ్యాస్ స్టవ్: https://youtu.be/tOYnCiG9qTY
పోర్టబుల్ గ్యాస్ స్టవ్ ఉపయోగం:https://youtu.be/2_NpKyRESEk
ఎలక్ట్రిక్ కుక్కర్: https://youtu.be/IzIIqIUGMBo
హ్యాండ్ హెల్డ్ వాక్యూమ్ క్లీనర్:https://youtu.be/gv0GiO_jUfs
రోబో వాక్యూమ్ క్లీనర్:https://youtu.be/_35n0gE-slo
వివిధ రకాల బ్లెండర్స్: https://youtu.be/Lc1BJglzNo0
                                       https://youtu.be/QeFydIXWGuc

నూతన గృహ డిజైన్ కు ఉపకరించే సూచనలు
ఇంటిని ఎలా డిజైన్ చేసుకోవాలి పార్ట్-1:https://youtu.be/MgHBx-_NMbk  
ఇంటిని ఎలా డిజైన్ చేసుకోవాలి పార్ట్-2:https://youtu.be/_CRYF3W2DYE
ఇంటిని ఎలా సర్దుకుంటే తేలిగ్గా ఉంటుంది 
పార్ట్-1: https://youtu.be/XkKhQ3hi9OY
పార్ట్-2:https://youtu.be/6jmpWs05Byc
వంటగదిని ఎలా సర్దుకోవచ్చు?
పార్ట్-1:https://youtu.be/13GknJeRBEU
పార్ట్-2:https://youtu.be/CtNV4KpDVGI

Episode 155: The Kidnapper's Game
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Aradhna is trapped inside a secret room by a mysterious kidnapper. Vikram and Pooja find a bloody trunk outside their house. The kidnapper threatens Reyansh to stop his investigation if he wants Aradhna to live. Meanwhile, Bhakti starts to regain her consciousness.

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

About*

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel.
